{"tid":1685834,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（擺食）無恥老翻香港吳留手","createTime":"2019-10-31T19:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:00:42.000Z","uid":2104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db1eaf0b543e12e403fc3a90569bbe1f9139d666","tid":1685834,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"黃埔一向有不少餐廳，不過大多數都收得頗早，最近開業的吳留手，就由下午開到凌晨，填補了這片空間。<br />\n<br />\n串燒種類多，肉類菜類海鮮通通有齊，一共超過80款。鹽燒盲鰽($108)在串燒店不常見，肉質飽滿厚實，每日新鮮取貨，肉質滑溜。原條茄子($35)燒得軟熟，帶濃烈蒜味，辛辣開胃。其他基本款式的串燒亦多選擇，如十三香雞中翼($19/2隻)、雞軟骨($23/2串)、鹿兒一口豚($39等)，口味多，即叫即燒，雖然不算入味，但價錢便宜抵食。<br />\n<br />\n吳留手還有不少水果菜式，菠蘿($21)燒得多汁香甜，炸香蕉($14/2)即叫即炸，煙韌香甜。雖然沒有特別款式，但區內街坊想吃消夜時，也是不錯選擇。提提大家，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n記者：李詠儀<br />\n攝影：陳秉謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳留手<br />\n地址：九龍黃埔必嘉街87號地舖<br />\n電話：6296 1628<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_59787756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_59787756&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4ePno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=dacd0e7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_59787756</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁樣仲成世界嘅！<br />\n而家攪到香港同大陸冇分別！<br />\n見人哋個名好就直接照抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家一齊抵制擺食老翻食店！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"70e12938a02b2d81de26c10ac7a707df350510fa","tid":1685834,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"黃埔一向有不少餐廳，不過大多數都收得頗早，最近開業的吳留手，就由下午開到凌晨，填補了這片空間。<br />\n<br />\n串燒種類多，肉類菜類海鮮通通有齊，一共超過80款。鹽燒盲鰽($108)在串燒店不常見，肉質飽滿厚實，每日新鮮取貨，肉質滑溜。原條茄子($35)燒得軟熟，帶濃烈蒜味，辛辣開胃。其他基本款式的串燒亦多選擇，如十三香雞中翼($19/2隻)、雞軟骨($23/2串)、鹿兒一口豚($39等)，口味多，即叫即燒，雖然不算入味，但價錢便宜抵食。<br />\n<br />\n吳留手還有不少水果菜式，菠蘿($21)燒得多汁香甜，炸香蕉($14/2)即叫即炸，煙韌香甜。雖然沒有特別款式，但區內街坊想吃消夜時，也是不錯選擇。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">提提大家，台灣雖有同名餐廳，但跟香港店完全沒有關係。</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb04a472e4d7bad440c98f923140a01d016479b0","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"呢間黃店黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9ca61dbbc0c6aa746a7c4f5feeec982bce8edf","tid":1685834,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb04a472e4d7bad440c98f923140a01d016479b0","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"呢間黃店黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"你話係就係？"},{"pid":"43c506d36f2582008dc7b03c2fe851b2d997927a","tid":1685834,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93025274b781e86b5609b4027b8882b1752f1099","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b9ca61dbbc0c6aa746a7c4f5feeec982bce8edf","tid":1685834,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb04a472e4d7bad440c98f923140a01d016479b0","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"呢間黃店黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"你話係就係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T00:38:42.000Z","msg":"自己睇map"},{"pid":"b525faab64385466260444b55196968409cb5cd7","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43c506d36f2582008dc7b03c2fe851b2d997927a","tid":1685834,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb04a472e4d7bad440c98f923140a01d016479b0","tid":1685834,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:58:55.000Z","msg":"呢間黃店黎<img src=\"/a